item.title: 【Off-Topic】What if iCarly had ending taglines like Victorious?
item.description:
Soooo I've been watching Victorious for the first time lately (yes, i've never watched it fully... SORRY) and I love Nick shows (please don't kill me, i know what used to happen on the set) and I was wondering: what would these ending taglines be if they were on iCarly?

So that's the point of this thread. If you find it cool, answer this with a quote from any episode of iCarly (and the name of the episode) cuz maybe I'm fan editing them...

and if you don't care just go to another post ;)

bye bye thanks
